description: With California Facts, you can learn about the state of California. Simply ask Alexa to start California Facts and you will learn more about California - things such as: the state flower, the state bird, and the state tree.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask california facts to give me a fact about California.
Alexa, ask california facts to tell me something.
Alexa, ask california facts to tell me a fact.
name: California Facts
shortDescription: Learn about the state of California.
